    "vendors": [
      {
        "about": "<ol start=\"1\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li>Key members of the team and major projects</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>***The MyHorse App has over 70 mil downloads on the app store, that is a big deal it shows user retention and scale</p>\r\n<p>The others speak for themselves</p>\r\n<p>Kevin Coghlan &ndash; Principal Coghlan Technology Group</p>\r\n<p>Joe Kubiak &ndash; Kubiak LLC &ndash; CV is attached and other projects are pasted above</p>\r\n<p>***I imagine you have an NDA in place with this investment bank, IF YOU DO NOT PLEASE DO NOT MENTION THE PRESIDENT TRUMP PROJECT.&nbsp; If you do, it is ok.&nbsp; That is going to be announced anyday now.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<ol start=\"2\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li>Native American Casino projects and any notable resources within the tribal community (this is big to prove our connections with potential franchise buyers)&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Coghlan Technology Group is working with one of the largest grossing casinos in the US, Thunder Valley Casino in Sacramento and Meskwaki Casino in Iowa as a full capacity innovation group.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Kevin&rsquo;s company has hosted/moderated an Innovation Panel at NIGA (the largest Indian Gaming Tradeshow in the US) in 2023 and will be speaking again on a panel.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(You should also mention Gary as well)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Members include:</p>\r\n<p>Kevin Coghlan &ndash; Principal</p>\r\n<p>Seth Eaton &ndash; MBA (USC Marshall School of Business), CCIE</p>\r\n<p>Joe Kubiak &ndash; attached and above</p>\r\n<p>Ethan Smith, MA &ndash; data scientist (Ethan is in the process of receiving his 2<sup>nd</sup>&nbsp;masters from the University of Pennsylvanis)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ol start=\"3\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li>Overview of major objectives for the FGL project</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>To use the past projects that Kubiak LLC has executed and build a custom application (mobile and web based) to accommodate all of the needs of the FLI Golf league and all associated analytics and building the foundation for scale and future enhancements of any associated activity needed (if you look at the attached you will see that Joe&rsquo;s team has already built the tech in other more advanced spaces, this project will be rather easy for him and his team based on the complexity of other projects they have executed.&nbsp; You have frontier technology experts building your platform.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ol start=\"4\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li>Timeline for completion and major check points</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Based on funding &ndash; this project can be built entirely and deployed in less than a month, full blown and extensive.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>However:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>***We recommend building it out piecemeal based on need and funding&hellip;you won&rsquo;t need all of the features and functionality in the beginning and we would advise against that approach anyway.&nbsp; The goal is you have a development partner that grows with you in a manner that is fiduciary and grows with the needs of the business as the league grows</p>\r\n</div>",
        "active": true,
