      {
        "about": "<h3>EXPERIENCE YOU CAN TRUST</h3>\r\n<div title=\"Page 1\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>From the courts of the NBA to the streets of F1 Racing, we have been there for your heart pounding moments. Pure Mobile Productions is trusted to bring clean broadcasts across an array of entertainment events. We have provided live broadcasts for the NBA, MLS, NWSL, College Sports, The Golf Channel and MMA Events to name a few. Our team is also the perfect match for live concerts. We have been on stage with some of the greatest names in music.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>",
